NK118(se)001:1: // rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK118(se)001:2: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa zhes bya ba'i
NK118(se)001:5: dpal ldan tshogs gnyis chu gter bsrubs pa las //
NK118(se)001:6: mkhyen brtse'i 'od dkar nges gsang gru char 'bebs //
NK118(se)001:7: gangs can mkhas grub yongs kyi gtsug rgyan mchog /
NK118(se)001:8: mtsho skyes rdo rje 'gro ba'i bla mar 'dud //
NK118(se)001:9: 'gro blo'i dri ma 'khrud mkhas drang srong gis //
NK118(se)001:10: blo gros beed+aura bum bzang rab thogs nas //
NK118(se)001:11: legs bshad sdom gsum bdud rtsi'i chu sbyin gyi //
NK118(se)001:12: don gnyer skye bo'i tshogs rnams 'dir 'dus shig /
NK118(se)001:13: rdzogs pa chen po ye shes spyi yi gzugs //
NK118(se)001:14: yongs su dag sku rdo rje 'chang chen po //
NK118(se)001:15: 'bras bu'i mthar thug sangs rgyas nyag gcig de //
NK118(se)001:16: zab rgyas chos kyi sgo 'phar bgrang yas kyang //
NK118(se)001:17: gsang chen smin grol lam mchog ma bsten par //
NK118(se)001:18: thob pa min zhes rdzogs sangs rgyas des gsungs //
NK118(se)001:19: ji srid sems kyi 'jug pa ma zad bar //
NK118(se)001:20: bsam yas theg pa'i grangs mthar thug pa med //
NK118(se)001:21: bgrod cig lam la bkri ba'i ngal stegs te //
NK118(se)001:22: rang rang rjes mthun 'bras bu bla dang bcas //
NK118(se)001:23: thob kyang theg pa so so'i nges 'byung las //
NK118(se)001:24: theg gcig lam la ma zhugs 'bras thob ci //
NK118(se)001:25: 'dir ni rdzogs pa chen po'i ring lugs ltar //
NK118(se)001:26: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK118(se)001:27: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa gsum zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)001:28: kri ya u pa yo ga phyi rgyud gsum //
NK118(se)001:29: bla med pha rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang //
NK118(se)001:30: ma rgyud a nu yo gar grags pa dang //
NK118(se)001:31: gnyis med rgyud sde a ti yo ga la //
NK118(se)001:32: nang rgyud gsum zhes theg pa rim dgur bsdu //
NK118(se)001:33: nyan rang byang sems rigs can so so la //
NK118(se)001:34: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i lam zhugs yod do zhes //
NK118(se)001:35: 'bum lnga'i rgyud kyi lung las gsal bar grub //
NK118(se)001:36: bsam pa'i dbye bas sngags la 'jug pa'i tshul //
NK118(se)001:37: chos sgo mang yang de dag spro bya min //
NK118(se)001:38: 'dir ni dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum las //
NK118(se)001:39: rab mchog sbyangs pa mthar son skal ldan te //
NK118(se)001:40: dbang bskur thob pas sdom gsum gcig car skyes //
NK118(se)001:41: rtogs grol dus mnyam in+d+ra b+h+au ti bzhin //
NK118(se)001:42: 'bring ni sdom gsum so so'i cho ga la //
NK118(se)001:43: brten nas rim thob n+aa gardzu na ltar //
NK118(se)001:44: tha ma skal dman shin tu gdul dka' de //
NK118(se)001:45: gso sbyong bslab pa'i gnas bcu grub mtha' bzhi //
NK118(se)001:46: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud kun rim shes nas //
NK118(se)001:47: bla med 'jug pa'i brtag pa gnyis par gsungs //
NK118(se)001:48: 'dir ni dbang po 'bring gi tshul 'chad de //
NK118(se)001:49: dge slong dge tshul dge bsnyen sdom ldan de //
NK118(se)001:50: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rab 'bring tha yin zhes //
NK118(se)001:51: phur pa'i rgyud dang dus 'khor las gsungs shing //
NK118(se)001:52: 'on kyang ye shes ldan pa gtso bor bzung //
NK118(se)001:53: snga 'gyur rgyud sde'i rtsa ba kun 'dus las //
NK118(se)001:54: rang dang gzhan don phan pa che bshad pa //
NK118(se)001:55: so thar sems bskyed dbang bskur nyid yin te //
NK118(se)001:56: so sor 'dzin na nyan thos byang sems dang //
NK118(se)001:57: rig pa 'dzin pa zhes su mkhas la grags //
NK118(se)001:58: de ltar thun mong sdom pa 'og ma gnyis //
NK118(se)001:59: 'dir ni bla med dbang gi yan lag tu //
NK118(se)001:60: rgyud sde rgya mtshor bshad ltar 'dir 'chad do //
NK118(se)001:61: sdom gsum so sor khog dbub gleng gzhi dang //
NK118(se)001:62: dang por sdom pa ma thob thob pa'i tshul //
NK118(se)001:63: bar du thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs //
NK118(se)001:64: tha mar nyams na gso tshul bzhi res sdom //
NK118(se)001:65: sdom gsum spyi'i bshad gzhi'i rim par phye ba ste dang po'o ////
NK118(se)001:66: gleng gzhi ston pas w+aa ra n+aa s+ai ru //
NK118(se)001:67: lhag pa'i tshul khrims gtsor ston bden pa bzhi //
NK118(se)001:68: lnga sder gsungs pa 'od srungs sogs kyis bsdus //
NK118(se)001:69: bye brag bshad mdzod la sogs 'phags pas brtsams //
NK118(se)001:70: yon tan 'od dang sh+aakya 'od kyis spel //
NK118(se)001:71: snga 'gyur sdom rgyun zhi ba 'tsho dang ni //
NK118(se)001:72: phyis nas sh+aakya sh+r+ai las kyang dar //
NK118(se)001:73: ngo bo nges 'byung bsam pas kun bslangs nas //
NK118(se)001:74: gzhan gnod gzhi bcas ldog pa lus ngag las //
NK118(se)001:75: skye phyir gzugs can yin ces 'dod pa dang //
NK118(se)001:76: spong sems rgyun chags sa bon la 'dod pa //
NK118(se)001:77: rang gi sde pa gong 'og so so'i lugs //
NK118(se)001:78: dbye ba bsnyen gnas dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis //
NK118(se)001:79: khyim pa'i phyogs yin dge tshul pha ma dang //
NK118(se)001:80: dge slong ma dang dge slong pha ma lnga //
NK118(se)001:81: rab byung la yin so thar ris brgyad po //
NK118(se)001:82: rdzas su bsdu na bzhir 'dod mdzod kyi lugs //
NK118(se)001:83: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob tshul la //
NK118(se)001:84: len tshul gnyis te sngon gyi cho ga ni //
NK118(se)001:85: rang byung ye shes khong chud 'phrin gyis rdzogs //
NK118(se)001:86: ston par khas blangs tshur shog gsol bzhi dang //
NK118(se)001:87: dris pa'i lan ldon lci chos khas blangs sogs //
NK118(se)001:88: gdug bya blo dag mkhan po 'phags pas yin //
NK118(se)001:89: da lta'i cho ga nges pa lnga bral zhing //
NK118(se)001:90: ma ning la sogs skye ba'i bar chad dang //
NK118(se)001:91: rgyal pos ma gnang la sogs gnas pa dang //
NK118(se)001:92: bya rog skrod mi nus sogs khyad par dang //
NK118(se)001:93: skra ser can sogs mdzes pa'i bar chad med //
NK118(se)001:94: nges 'byung blo can skal bzang skyes bu de //
NK118(se)001:95: legs gsungs 'dul ba rgya mtsho mtha' dag dang //
NK118(se)001:96: brgya rtsa gcig pa'i las phran la byang ba'i //
NK118(se)001:97: mkhan por bcas pas rim bzhin bsnyen par rdzogs //
NK118(se)001:98: snga ma ma byas rdzogs pa'am mdo sder snang //
NK118(se)001:99: thob mtshams brjod pa gsum gyi mtha' mar 'dod //
NK118(se)001:100: bar du thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba la //
NK118(se)001:101: bslab bya skyabs 'gro thun mong min gsum ni //
NK118(se)001:102: skyabs gzhan mi 'tshol sems can 'tshe ba spong //
NK118(se)001:103: mu stegs mi 'grogs so sor gus bskyed do //
NK118(se)001:104: srog dang bya dkar dkon mchog gsum mi spang //
NK118(se)001:105: dgos gal che yang thabs gzhan mi 'tshol zhing //
NK118(se)001:106: dus mchod mi bcag rang gzhan skyabs 'gror 'god //
NK118(se)001:107: gar 'gro'i phyogs kyi sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal //
NK118(se)001:108: lnga rnams thun mong bslab byar jo bo bzhed //
NK118(se)001:109: rtsa bzhi spong ba tshul khrims yan lag bzhi //
NK118(se)001:110: chang spang bag yod yan lag mal che mtho //
NK118(se)001:111: gar phreng la sogs phyi dro'i kha zas gsum //
NK118(se)001:112: brtul zhugs yan lag bsnyen gnas sdom pa yin //
NK118(se)001:113: yan lag 'di brgyad gtan du ma yin pas //
NK118(se)001:114: yon tan rten min de phyir so thar ni //
NK118(se)001:115: mtshan nyid ldan pa rigs bdun kho na yin //
NK118(se)001:116: 'di brgyad ji srid 'tsho ba'i bar bsrungs na //
NK118(se)001:117: go mi'i dge bsnyen yin kyang yod smra'i min //
NK118(se)001:118: gnas brtan sde pa'i lugs su dbyig gnyen bzhed //
NK118(se)001:119: gsod rku rdzun smra 'dod pas log par g.yem //
NK118(se)001:120: myos 'gyur spong rnams dge bsnyen sdom pa ste //
NK118(se)001:121: gang 'dod khas len grangs ltar sna gcig spyod //
NK118(se)001:122: sna 'ga' phal cher spyod dang yongs rdzogs spyod //
NK118(se)001:123: gcig gnyis gsum dang lnga spangs de yi steng //
NK118(se)001:124: mi tshangs spyod spong tshangs spyod dge bsten no //
NK118(se)001:125: 'di dang go mi gnyis ni khyim pa dang //
NK118(se)001:126: rab byung gnyis ka min zhes mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK118(se)001:127: mi dge lhag drug phyogs mthun spang bya dang //
NK118(se)001:128: dge bsnyen sdom ldan rig pa 'dzin pas kyang //
NK118(se)001:129: rab byung rtags dang cho ga ma gtogs pa //
NK118(se)001:130: lhag rnams nyams su len par dpung bzang bshad //
NK118(se)001:131: srog gcod rku dang mi tshangs spyod dang rdzun //
NK118(se)001:132: chang 'thung gar sogs phreng sogs mal che mtho //
NK118(se)001:133: phyi dro'i kha zas gser dngul spong ba ste //
NK118(se)001:134: zhum pa spang phyir rags pa bcur dril gsungs //
NK118(se)001:135: chos gos lhung bzed 'chang ba 'bral ba dang //
NK118(se)001:136: sa rko rin chen reg dang me la reg /
NK118(se)001:137: spangs nas za dang shing 'dzeg shing gcod dang //
NK118(se)001:138: byin len r+ts+wa sngon khrod du mi gtsang 'dor //
NK118(se)001:139: gsog 'jog za dang sa bon 'joms pa rnams //
NK118(se)001:140: gnang bas nyes med bcu gsum ma gtogs pa //
NK118(se)001:141: dge slong ji bzhin spang blang mtha' dag gcig /'chang
NK118(se)001:142: ba'i zlar bsdu gos rgyu zla bar 'jog /'bral ba'i
NK118(se)001:143: zlar bsdu dgon pa'i 'bras spang byed //
NK118(se)001:144: gsog 'jog zlar bsdu gsog 'jog byed pa'ang gnang //
NK118(se)001:145: khyim rtags spong nyams rab byung rtags len nyams //
NK118(se)001:146: brnyas pas mkhan por nyams te nyams pa gsum //
NK118(se)001:147: spang ba dge tshul sdom pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK118(se)001:148: dge slob ma ni dge tshul thob pa'i steng //
NK118(se)001:149: gcig 'gro chur rkyal skyes reg lhan cig 'dug /
NK118(se)001:150: smyan bya nyes 'chab rtsa ba'i chos drug go //
NK118(se)001:151: gser bzung 'doms spu 'dreg dang sa brko spang //
NK118(se)001:152: byin len med dang gsog 'jog byas mi za //
NK118(se)001:153: r+ts+wa sngon mi gcod 'di rnams rjes mthun drug /
NK118(se)001:154: dge slong khrims la nyis brgya lnga bcu gsum //
NK118(se)001:155: sdom pa'i rtsa ba pham pa bzhi zhes pa //
NK118(se)001:156: gzhi yi yan lag cha kun bzung 'os pa //
NK118(se)001:157: skye gnas lam du pho dbang las rung ni //
NK118(se)001:158: bsam pa ngo tsha 'jigs med chags sems kyis //
NK118(se)001:159: sbyor ba drud pa mthar thug sim pa thob //
NK118(se)001:160: des ni tshangs par spyod las rnam par nyams //
NK118(se)001:161: brku ba'i gzhi ni mi gzhan nor yin pa //
NK118(se)001:162: bsam pa rang nyid 'tsho phyir brku sems kyis //
NK118(se)001:163: yul dus rin thang tshang ba sbyor bas brkus //
NK118(se)001:164: mthar thug brkus sam brkur bcug rtsad nas thob //
NK118(se)001:165: srog gcod gzhi ni mi gzhan ma 'khrul par //
NK118(se)001:166: bsam pa gsod sems gsad bya der shes pa //
NK118(se)001:167: sbyor ba gsod par brtsams nas ma bzlog pa //
NK118(se)001:168: mthar thug srog gi dbang po 'gags pa dang //
NK118(se)001:169: gsod bcug yi rang sngags sogs rkyen byas kyang //
NK118(se)001:170: rdzun gyi gzhi ni smra shes don go'i mir //
NK118(se)001:171: bsam pa 'du shes bsgyur nas brjod blo skyes //
NK118(se)001:172: sbyor ba mngon shes pa sogs yon tan tshogs //
NK118(se)001:173: med kyang yod ces bla ma'i rdzun smras pa //
NK118(se)001:174: mthar thug gzhan gyis rdzun de go na nyams //
NK118(se)001:175: 'di bzhi gang spyad dge slong de pham phyir //
NK118(se)001:176: phas pham bzhi zhes thams cad mkhyen des gsungs //
NK118(se)001:177: dge 'dun lhag ma bcu gsum zhes grags pa //
NK118(se)001:178: bsgrod min gnas su khu ba 'byin pa dang //
NK118(se)001:179: chags pas bud med lus kyi cha shas 'dzin //
NK118(se)001:180: 'khrig tshig rjen smra bud med chags phyir bkur //
NK118(se)001:181: pho mo phan tshun smyan byas 'dus te 'phrad //
NK118(se)001:182: rang don tshad lhag khang pa khang chen brtsigs //
NK118(se)001:183: brjod gzhi med dang snyad ka bag tsam la //
NK118(se)001:184: brten nas dge slong skur btab dge 'dun dbyen //
NK118(se)001:185: dbyen de'i rjes phyogs bslab pa dang 'gal ba //
NK118(se)001:186: khyim sun 'byin tshe skrod byed la snyon pa //
NK118(se)001:187: ltung byung bskul tshe bka' blo mi bde ba'o //
NK118(se)001:188: spang ba ltung byed sum cu'i sde bshad pa //
NK118(se)001:189: rang gi gos lhag zhag bcu 'das par 'chang //
NK118(se)001:190: chos gos dang bral zhag gcig lon pa dang //
NK118(se)001:191: gos rgyu zla gcig 'jog dang dge slong mar //
NK118(se)001:192: chos gos 'khrur 'jug de la gos rgyu len //
NK118(se)001:193: nye min khyim par gos rgyu slong ba dang //
NK118(se)001:194: ster na stod g.yogs smad g.yogs lhag por len //
NK118(se)001:195: rang la ster bsam chos gos gnas dpags pa //
NK118(se)001:196: rin dang khru tshad kyis slong rtags dran slong //
NK118(se)001:197: gos rin rin chen bskur ba len rnams so //
NK118(se)001:198: srin bal nang tshang byas pa'i stan byed dang //
NK118(se)001:199: dkon sar bal nag 'ba' zhig stan du 'dings //
NK118(se)001:200: bal nag cha gnyis stan byed lo drug ni //
NK118(se)001:201: ma song stan gsar byed dang tshad ldan gyi //
NK118(se)001:202: 'ding ba yod kyang slar bzo bal nag ni //
NK118(se)001:203: rnyed nas lam gyi dpag tshad gsum mthar byed //
NK118(se)001:204: dge slong mar ni bal 'khru rmel bcug dang //
NK118(se)001:205: gser dngul len dang tshong 'bun mngon mtshan can //
NK118(se)001:206: ched du tshong byed lhung bzed byin ma brlabs //
NK118(se)001:207: zhag bcu 'das 'char lhung bzed zung 'chang ba //
NK118(se)001:208: gla rngan med par 'thag 'jug thags rgya bskyed //
NK118(se)001:209: dge slong gos byin slar phrogs gtad byung gos //
NK118(se)001:210: sbyin dus bshad las snga bar bdag gir byas //
NK118(se)001:211: dgon par 'jigs bcas gos bral zhag bdun 'das //
NK118(se)001:212: ras chen dgag dbye zin kyang zla phyed 'das //
NK118(se)001:213: dge 'dun bsngosa pa'i rnyed pa bdag tu bzung //
NK118(se)001:214: na sman zhag bdun 'das nas gsog 'jog go //
NK118(se)001:215: ltung byed 'ba' zhig dgu bcu tham pa ni //
NK118(se)001:216: shes bzhin rdzun smra dge slong skyon brjod pa //
NK118(se)001:217: phra mas 'byed dang skyo sngogs bzlums kyang dbye //
NK118(se)001:218: bud med chos ston bsnyen par ma rdzogs dang //
NK118(se)001:219: lhan cig chos 'don gnas ngan len ltung brjod //
NK118(se)001:220: mi chos bla ma bden smra bshes ngor 'phya //
NK118(se)001:221: bslab gzhi khyad gsod sa bon skye ba gcod //
NK118(se)001:222: bdag gi ngor 'phya bsgo ba rnar gzon ni //
NK118(se)001:223: ltung byung gleng la ma thos lan gzhan 'debs //
NK118(se)001:224: khri dang 'ding ba ma bsdus gting song dang //
NK118(se)001:225: dge slong skrod dang tho 'tshams phyis gnon byas //
NK118(se)001:226: mal khris bug dbyung srog chags ldan pa'i chu //
NK118(se)001:227: r+ts+war 'debs gtsug lag pha gu rim gnyis brtsig /
NK118(se)001:228: shes bzhin bgyis so 'di man dge slong mar //
NK118(se)001:229: ma bskos chos ston bskos kyang nyi nub dang //
NK118(se)001:230: kha zas phyir ston gos brtsems chos gos sbyin //
NK118(se)001:231: don mthun lam 'grogs gru de gyen mthur 'gro //
NK118(se)001:232: dben par gcig 'dug pa dang 'greng ba dang /
NK118(se)001:233: sbyor bcug zas za rnams ni spang bar bya //
NK118(se)001:234: yang yang zas za mu stegs 'dug pa'i sar //
NK118(se)001:235: zhag gcig lhag bsdad za dang lhung bzed do //
NK118(se)001:236: za dang zos rjes bza' bca' za ba dang //
NK118(se)001:237: spang zas ltung 'byung ched du rdzun gyis stob //
NK118(se)001:238: gnang min mtshams nang logs su 'dus nas za //
NK118(se)001:239: dus min phyed yol za dang gsog 'jog za //
NK118(se)001:240: sbyin len ma byas sman bzhi khar mid pa //
NK118(se)001:241: bsod pa zhim pa'i zas slong srog chags bcas //
NK118(se)001:242: chur spyod nyal po byed pa'i shul du nyal //
NK118(se)001:243: dben pa'i skyabs su 'greng dang gcer bur rgyu //
NK118(se)001:244: dmag blta dmag sar zhag gnyis lhag pa bsdad //
NK118(se)001:245: dmag gi ru bkod byed dang dge slong brdeg /
NK118(se)001:246: brdeg brtsams gnas ngan len gyi ltung ba 'chab //
NK118(se)001:247: dge slong zas gcod me la reg tu bcug /
NK118(se)001:248: dge 'dun las la 'dun phul phyir ldog smra //
NK118(se)001:249: bsnyen ma rdzogs dang nub gnyis lhag par nyal //
NK118(se)001:250: sdig lta'i chos lugs mi gtong phebs par smra //
NK118(se)001:251: dge tshul sdig lta mi gtong lhan cig nyal //
NK118(se)001:252: rung ba'i tshon min kha dog can gos gyon //
NK118(se)001:253: rin chen dmag chas rol mo'i chas la reg /
NK118(se)001:254: tsha dus rang gar khrus byed dud 'gro gsod //
NK118(se)001:255: dge slong byas la 'gyod bskyed gag tshil sgog /
NK118(se)001:256: chur rtse bud med gnas gcig nyal ba dang //
NK118(se)001:257: dge slong dngangs byed de yi yo byad sbed //
NK118(se)001:258: sngar byin gding med slar blangs spyod pa dang //
NK118(se)001:259: gzhi med skur btab bud med lhan cig tu //
NK118(se)001:260: skyes pa med par lam 'gro rkun ma'ang mtshungs //
NK118(se)001:261: nyi shu ma lon pa la bsnyen rdzogs phog /
NK118(se)001:262: sa brko mgron bos zla bzhi lhag par zos //
NK118(se)001:263: mi shes brjod dang 'thab pa'i nyan rna byed //
NK118(se)001:264: nyes med mi smra 'gro dang mi gus 'gal //
NK118(se)001:265: chang 'thung dus min phyi dro grong du rgyu //
NK118(se)001:266: zas bcas phyi dro rgyu dang khyim gsum 'das //
NK118(se)001:267: rgyal po btsun mor rtse ba'i khab tu nyal //
NK118(se)001:268: mdo sogs 'don la da gdod shes zer dang //
NK118(se)001:269: rin chen khab ral khri rkang tshad lhag bzos //
NK118(se)001:270: ngan sems shing bal khri steng brdal te bgos //
NK118(se)001:271: gding g.yan ras chen chos gos tshad lhag go //
NK118(se)001:272: so sor bshags bya'i sde ni bzhi yin te //
NK118(se)001:273: dge slong ma las grong du zas bslangs zos //
NK118(se)001:274: khyim du dge slong mas bsgos ma bzlog zos //
NK118(se)001:275: bslab sdom sbyin las rung min bslangs te zos //
NK118(se)001:276: nags ma myul bar dgon par bslangs zos bzhi'o //
NK118(se)001:277: nyes byas brgya dang bcu gnyis zhes grags pa //
NK118(se)001:278: sham thabs zlum min brtsengs 'jol glang sna 'dra //
NK118(se)001:279: lteb dang phur ma gdengs ka lta bu 'dun //
NK118(se)001:280: zlum min ring thung stod gsum gos kyi bcu'o //
NK118(se)001:281: ma bsdams bgo ba ca co mig g.yengs dang //
NK118(se)001:282: ring blta mgo bstums gos barjesa phrag la gzar //
NK118(se)001:283: lag pa gnya' gong bsnol dang ltag par bsnol //
NK118(se)001:284: mchong rkyang rkang pa'i brang dang rting btsugs 'gro //
NK118(se)001:285: lag pa dkur brten lus bsgyur lag pa g.yug /
NK118(se)001:286: mgo bsgyur phrag pa sprad dang lag sbrel rnams //
NK118(se)001:287: mi byed khyim 'gro'i spyod yul nyi shu'o //
NK118(se)001:288: stan la ma bsgos ma brtags 'phongs rdeb dang //
NK118(se)001:289: rkang brkyang bsnol dang barla bsnol long bu brtsegs //
NK118(se)001:290: khri 'og rkang dgug rkang pa gdangs te 'dug /'doms mthong rnams spang 'dug tshul dgu yin no //
NK118(se)001:291: legs par mi len mu kha mnyam par len //
NK118(se)001:292: mthar chags mi len lhung bzed zur mig blta //
NK118(se)001:293: bzed sngas sngar byung sbas nas bzed pa dang //
NK118(se)001:294: snod gzhan steng bzed spang ba zas blang brgyad //
NK118(se)001:295: 'gal za kham che chung dang ran par min //
NK118(se)001:296: kha gdangs za bzhin smra dang tsug tsug dang //
NK118(se)001:297: cag cag hu hu phu phu lce phyung za //
NK118(se)001:298: 'bru nas gud phye zas la skyon 'phya dang //
NK118(se)001:299: kham gcig mkhur spo rkan tog kham 'phro bcad //
NK118(se)001:300: lag pa ldag 'byog lag sprug skyom skyom byed //
NK118(se)001:301: mchod rten 'drar byed nyer gcig za tshe spang //
NK118(se)001:302: lhung bzed la 'phya phyir blta lag pa ni //
NK118(se)001:303: zas 'bags chu snod mi reg chu mi gtor //
NK118(se)001:304: ma 'dres 'bags chu 'bo dang zas lhag bzhag /
NK118(se)001:305: sa rjes gad kha ri gzar bang rim bzhir //
NK118(se)001:306: mi bzhag gdag yang rkan gzar du mi 'khru //
NK118(se)001:307: langs dang chu drag mi gcu bcu bzhi'o //
NK118(se)001:308: chos ston sde ni langs nyal rang dmar 'dug /
NK118(se)001:309: mdun nas 'gro la phyi bshad lam po'i 'gram //
NK118(se)001:310: mgo g.yogs bardzesa gzar lag pa gnya' ltag bsnol //
NK118(se)001:311: do ker bcings dang zhwa gyon cod pan btags //
NK118(se)001:312: phreng ba dang ni mgo dkris glang rta zhon //
NK118(se)001:313: khyogs dang bzhon pa mchil lhwam gyon pa dang //
NK118(se)001:314: 'khar ba gdugs mtshon ral gri dgra cha mda' //
NK118(se)001:315: go cha gyon la mi bshad nyer drug go //
NK118(se)001:316: sgrub tshul gsum ni 'grengs te bshad gci 'dor //
NK118(se)001:317: chu dang r+ts+wa la bshang gci snabs mi 'dor //
NK118(se)001:318: shing la mi gang mthor 'dzeg rgyu gcig go //
NK118(se)001:319: dge slong ma la pham brgyad lhag nyi shu //
NK118(se)001:320: spang ltung so gsum ltung byed brgya brgyad cu //
NK118(se)001:321: so gshags bcu gcig nyes byas brgya bcu gnyis //
NK118(se)001:322: sum brgya drug cu rtsa bzhi mdo tsam mo //
NK118(se)001:323: sgrub pa'i bslab bya yongs su sbyong ba'i tshul //
NK118(se)001:324: gso sbyong dbyar gnas dgag dbye gos kyi gzhi //
NK118(se)001:325: ko lpags gnas mal sman sogs gzhan du shes //
NK118(se)001:326: mdor na ye nas gnang dang bkag pa med //
NK118(se)001:327: byar rung dang nye mi rung ldog byed na //
NK118(se)001:328: de dag spyod cig mi rung dang nye zhing //
NK118(se)001:329: rung ba bzlog na kun tu spong zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)001:330: skye ba'i rten ni mu stegs mtshams med byas //
NK118(se)001:331: sgra mi snyan dang za ma mtshan gnyis dang //
NK118(se)001:332: ma ning rigs lnga mtshan gsum gyur pa dang //
NK118(se)001:333: sprul pa ma gtogs gling gsum skyes pa yi //
NK118(se)001:334: skyes pa bud med sdom pa'i rten du 'dod //
NK118(se)001:335: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK118(se)001:336: gtong ba bslab pa phul dang shi 'phos dang //
NK118(se)001:337: mtshan gnyis gcig car byung dang lan gsum gyur //
NK118(se)001:338: rgyu 'bras med bltas rtsa ba chad rnams lci //
NK118(se)001:339: nyi shu ma lon bsnyen rdzogs rjes su shes //
NK118(se)001:340: dge slong sdom gtong rten phyir khas blangs 'das //
NK118(se)001:341: dge slong ma'o mtshan 'das bsnyen gnas kyi //
NK118(se)001:342: sdom pa gtong rnams so sos thun mong min //
NK118(se)001:343: rtsa ltung byung dang dam chos nub na'ang gtong //
NK118(se)001:344: kha che'i yul gyi bye brag smra ba rnams //
NK118(se)001:345: sdom ldan rtsa ltung byung ba gnyis ldan na //
NK118(se)001:346: nor ldan bu lon can bzhin 'dod pa dang //
NK118(se)001:347: kha cig rtsa bzhi gcig spyad kun nyams zer //
NK118(se)001:348: dang po'i las can sems 'khrugs tshor bas gzir //
NK118(se)001:349: sgrub par ma nus pa la nyes pa med //
NK118(se)001:350: 'chab pa zhes grags gsang ste mi brjod pa //
NK118(se)001:351: pham pa 'chab bcas tshe 'dir gsor mi rung //
NK118(se)001:352: 'chab pa med na dngos po brjod pa yis //
NK118(se)001:353: dge 'dun la bshags mthong sdom bar gyis 'dag /
NK118(se)001:354: sdom pa slar nod lhag ma bcu gsum sogs //
NK118(se)001:355: lci yang la ltos bshags te rim par ldang //
NK118(se)001:356: mdor na stobs bzhir ma 'dus bshags pa med //
NK118(se)001:357: sngar byas 'gyod bshags khong du dug song ltar //
NK118(se)001:358: 'gyod pa snying nas rnam par sun 'byin stobs //
NK118(se)001:359: dug la sman bzhin 'jug pa drag po yis //
NK118(se)001:360: nyes phyir dge ba'i gnyen po kun spyod stobs //
NK118(se)001:361: dug mi 'thung ltar phyis nas nyes sdom la //
NK118(se)001:362: nges shes drag po rnam par sor chud stobs //
NK118(se)001:363: sman pa bsten ltar skyabs sems ltung bshags sogs //
NK118(se)001:364: dad pa drag pos rten gyi stobs bzhi spyad //
NK118(se)001:365: 'on kyang sdig ltung stobs ldan res spyod na //
NK118(se)001:366: sa thob yun du 'gor bas mig ltar bsrung //
NK118(se)001:367: phan yon nad dang rgyal po'i chad phyir blangs //
NK118(se)001:368: rkyen 'ga' sel kyang 'jigs skyobs tshul khrims yin //
NK118(se)001:369: phyi ma'i ched blangs legs smon tshul khrims zhes //
NK118(se)001:370: lha mi'i bde 'bras thob kyang thar pa min //
NK118(se)001:371: nges par 'byung ba'i tshul khrims sdom ldan na //
NK118(se)001:372: dgra bcom thob pa dga' bo'i rnam thar bzhin //
NK118(se)001:373: skyabs gsum 'dzin sogs yon tan phyi ma mchog /
NK118(se)001:374: snga ma phyi ma'i thun mong lam yin phyir //
NK118(se)001:375: sems bskyed sngags kyi gdul bya'ang de dang mtshungs //
NK118(se)001:376: de phyir yon tan kun gyi gzhi rten yin //
NK118(se)001:377: 'dul ba so thar gyi rim par phye ba ste gnyis pa'o ////
NK118(se)001:378: skal bzang 'gro ba'i 'dren pa thub chen des //
NK118(se)001:379: bya rgod phung sogs theg chen rigs can la //
NK118(se)001:380: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod dpag yas gsungs //
NK118(se)001:381: 'jam dbyangs bka' bsdus klu sgrub sogs kyis bkral //
NK118(se)001:382: zhi ba lhas spel zab mo lta ba'i lugs //
NK118(se)001:383: byams pas bka' bsdus thog med sku mched bkral //
NK118(se)001:384: jo bo rjes spel rgya chen spyod pa'i srol //
NK118(se)001:385: pad+ma'i ring lugs n+aa gardzu na mthun //
NK118(se)001:386: ngo bo byams dang snying rjes rgyud brlan cing //
NK118(se)001:387: gzhan gyi don du byang chub thob 'dod pas //
NK118(se)001:388: sgo gsum nyes pa spong ba'i sems pa'o //
NK118(se)001:389: dbye ba klu sgrub thogs med srol gnyis grags //
NK118(se)001:390: re re gcig nas drug par gnyis gnyis te //
NK118(se)001:391: dang po stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can //
NK118(se)001:392: tshogs gnyis bslab pa kun rdzob don dam gnyis //
NK118(se)001:393: tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab bslab gsum dang //
NK118(se)001:394: tshogs sbyor mos pas spyod pa'i sems bskyed dang //
NK118(se)001:395: ma dag sa bdun lhag bsam dag pa dang //
NK118(se)001:396: dag pa sa gsum rnam par smin pa dang //
NK118(se)001:397: thugs rje chen po sgrib kun spangs pa ni //
NK118(se)001:398: sangs rgyas sa yi sems bskyed dag dang bzhi //
NK118(se)001:399: lnga ni lam lnga drug ni phar phyin drug /
NK118(se)001:400: sa gser zla ba me sogs nyer gnyis ni //
NK118(se)001:401: sa mtshams kyis phye sa bcu'i bar du'o //
NK118(se)001:402: kun kyang bsdu na smon 'jug rnam pa gnyis //
NK118(se)001:403: de yang bsam pas smon dang sbyor bas khyab //
NK118(se)001:404: 'gro bar 'dod dang 'gro ba ji bzhin no //
NK118(se)001:405: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob tshul ni //
NK118(se)001:406: len tshul sdom gnas dge ba'i bshes gnyen la //
NK118(se)001:407: theg chen snod gyur dad ldan slob ma yis //
NK118(se)001:408: yan lag bdun mthar smon 'jug stabs gcig tu //
NK118(se)001:409: len cing rang gzhan dga' ba sgom pa rnams //
NK118(se)001:410: klu sgrub lugs yin thogs med bzhed pa ni //
NK118(se)001:411: smon sems len la so thar mi dgos kyang //
NK118(se)001:412: yang dag blangs pa rigs bdun sngon song nas //
NK118(se)001:413: bar chad dri dang bslab pa khas len sogs //
NK118(se)001:414: smon 'jug cho ga so so'i sgo nas len //
NK118(se)001:415: rgyal ba'i rten la'ang rung bar srol gnyis mthun //
NK118(se)001:416: thob mtshams brjod pa gsum gyi mtha' la'o //
NK118(se)001:417: don dam sems bskyed cho gas blangs thob pa //
NK118(se)001:418: gsang sngags lugs yin mdo las bshad srid na //
NK118(se)001:419: dam bca' nyid yin sgom pa'i stobs las skye //
NK118(se)001:420: bar du mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs bshad pa //
NK118(se)001:421: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims gsum yin te //
NK118(se)001:422: nyes spyod sdom dang dge ba chos sdud dang //
NK118(se)001:423: sems can don byed gsum las dang po ni //
NK118(se)001:424: dkon mchog dkor 'phrog dang ni chos spong las //
NK118(se)001:425: tshul ldan tshul 'chal khrims gcod bslab 'bebs sogs //
NK118(se)001:426: mtshams med las byed log lta lnga rgyal po //
NK118(se)001:427: grong ljongs grong khyer grol brdal yul 'khor rnams //
NK118(se)001:428: 'joms par byed pa'ang blon por nges pa lnga //
NK118(se)001:429: ma sbyangs stong nyid brjod sngas nyan thos smon //
NK118(se)001:430: rdzogs byang phyir ldog theg dman sems bskyed dang //
NK118(se)001:431: so thar spangs nas theg chen slob pa dang //
NK118(se)001:432: nyan thos theg pas chags sogs mi zlog pas //
NK118(se)001:433: de zlog de yi 'bras bu med par byas //
NK118(se)001:434: phrag dog dbang gis bdag bstod gzhan smod dang //
NK118(se)001:435: rnyed dang bkur sti'i ched du bdag 'tshong dang //
NK118(se)001:436: dge slong chad pas gcod 'jug sug 'bul dang //
NK118(se)001:437: spong ba'i longs spyod kha ton pa la byin //
NK118(se)001:438: zhi gnas 'dor bcug phal la 'byung nges brgyad //
NK118(se)001:439: de der 'byung nyes bzhag gi kun la kun //
NK118(se)001:440: ming du bco brgyad rdzas su bcu bzhi ste //
NK118(se)001:441: smon 'jug sems btang de rnams rtsa ltung yin //
NK118(se)001:442: yan lag nyes byas brgyad cu la sogs pa //
NK118(se)001:443: phra phyir 'dir ni ma bshad bslab btus blta //
NK118(se)001:444: thogs med lugs kyi smon pa'i bslab bya la //
NK118(se)001:445: sems can blos mi btang dang phan yon dran //
NK118(se)001:446: tshogs bsag byang sems sbyang la brtson pa dang //
NK118(se)001:447: dkar nag chos brgyad blang dor smon pa'i yin //
NK118(se)001:448: mchod 'os bslu dang 'gyod med 'gyod pa bskyed //
NK118(se)001:449: dam par sku 'debs 'gro la g.yo sgyus spyod //
NK118(se)001:450: nag po'i chos bzhi spang zhing ldog pa ni //
NK118(se)001:451: dkar po'i chos bzhi yin pas kun tu spyad //
NK118(se)001:452: rnyed bkur lhag zhen bdag bstod gzhan smod dang //
NK118(se)001:453: ser snas zang zing nor dang chos mi ster //
NK118(se)001:454: khro bos gzhan 'tshe shad sbyang gis mi ldog /
NK118(se)001:455: g.yom las chos ltar bcos mos ston pa bzhi //
NK118(se)001:456: rtsa ltung bzhi ste 'jug pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK118(se)001:457: nyes byas phra ba zhe drug gzhan du shes //
NK118(se)001:458: dge ba chos sdud phar phyin drug slob ste //
NK118(se)001:459: dbul ba sel phyir chos nor mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK118(se)001:460: spong ba'i sems kyis tshul khrims rnam gsum spyad //
NK118(se)001:461: khong khro zab mo sdug bsngal bzod par bya //
NK118(se)001:462: go cha dge sdud gzhan phan brtson 'grus brtsam //
NK118(se)001:463: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i bsam gtan bsgom //
NK118(se)001:464: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab zab mo spyad //
NK118(se)001:465: sems can don byed tshul khrims bsdu dngos bzhi //
NK118(se)001:466: thog mar sbyin pas gdul bya rab bsdus nas //
NK118(se)001:467: snyan par smra ba'i gtam gyis yid rab drang //
NK118(se)001:468: theg pa rim dgur bkri ba don spyod de //
NK118(se)001:469: de dag 'dren phyir rang yang don de spyod //
NK118(se)001:470: mthun phyogs kun slob mi mthun mtha' dag spang //
NK118(se)001:471: rtag tu dran dang shes bzhin bag yod bsten //
NK118(se)001:472: 'gro 'dug za nyal spyod lam rnam pa bzhir //
NK118(se)001:473: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i mdo sde ltar //
NK118(se)001:474: gang byed rigs mthun tshig gis smon lam 'debs //
NK118(se)001:475: mkhyen rab dbang phyug klong chen rab 'byams ni //
NK118(se)001:476: smon pa'i bslab bya tshad med bzhi bsgom zhing //
NK118(se)001:477: 'jug pa'i bslab bya pha rol phyin drug spyod //
NK118(se)001:478: bsdu na dkar nag chos brgyad 'du zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)001:479: 'dir ni phan dang bde ba rnams bya zhing //
NK118(se)001:480: 'dir yang mi phan phyi mar gnod pa spang //
NK118(se)001:481: srol gnyis bslab byar ma 'dus med ces smra //
NK118(se)001:482: skye ba'i rten ni lha klu 'phrog ma sogs //
NK118(se)001:483: sdig can la yang skye bar klu sgrub bzhed //
NK118(se)001:484: thogs med de'i rten so thar dgos zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)001:485: spyir na sangs rgyas chos la dad byed cing //
NK118(se)001:486: 'bras bu bla med byang chub la dad dang //
NK118(se)001:487: rgyal sras spyod pa rgya mtshor dad byed na //
NK118(se)001:488: byang sems skye bar dkon mchog t+aa lar gsungs //
NK118(se)001:489: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK118(se)001:490: gang gis rigs dang mi rigs ma brtags par //
NK118(se)001:491: rtsom mam ldog gam btang snyoms 'jog kyang rung //
NK118(se)001:492: 'os las 'das byed thams cad ltung ba'i sde //
NK118(se)001:493: don chen bsgrub la chung btang gzugs brnyan te //
NK118(se)001:494: nus pa'i yul min thams cad ltung ba med //
NK118(se)001:495: mi nus der brtson de yi gzugs brnyan yin //
NK118(se)001:496: gzhan phyir phan na lus ngag mi dge 'dun //
NK118(se)001:497: gnang ba'i skabs yod don la dge ba yin //
NK118(se)001:498: thun 'das nyams na 'phags pa nam snying la //
NK118(se)001:499: tho rangs gsol btab rmi lam ltung ba 'chags //
NK118(se)001:500: lhag ma phung po gsum pa nyin mtshan du //
NK118(se)001:501: lan gsum 'don pas gzhil ba klu sgrub lugs //
NK118(se)001:502: smon pa'i sems ni nag po'i chos bzhi spyad //
NK118(se)001:503: sems can snying nas blos btang de gtong 'gyur //
NK118(se)001:504: rgyun mi chad spyod ngo tsha khrel med dang //
NK118(se)001:505: des mgu dga' dang de nyid yon tan du //
NK118(se)001:506: lta ba kun dkris chen pos sdom pa 'joms //
NK118(se)001:507: pham pa zhes brjod chung dang 'bring la min //
NK118(se)001:508: phas pham byung na slar blang 'bring ni gsum //
NK118(se)001:509: tha ma gcig mdun dngos po brjod pas bshags //
NK118(se)001:510: mthun pa'i gang zag med na yid kyis bsdam //
NK118(se)001:511: rgya chen spyod pa'i ring lugs zla med do //
NK118(se)001:512: 'di 'dra'i byang chub sems kyi rtsis zin na //
NK118(se)001:513: gnyid sogs bag med gyur la'ang bsod nams shugs //
NK118(se)001:514: rgyun mi chad 'byung rgyal ba'i sras su 'gyur //
NK118(se)001:515: grangs med gsum bdun so gsum byang chub thob //
NK118(se)001:516: byang chub sems dpa'i sems bskyed kyi bslab bya bshad pa'i rim par phye ba ste gsum pa'o ////
NK118(se)001:517: kun bzang rdo rje 'chang dbang ston pa des //
NK118(se)001:518: 'og min chen por rgyud sde rgya mtsho gsungs //
NK118(se)001:519: phyis nas 'bras spungs sogs su bzlas te bstan //
NK118(se)001:520: phyag rdor dang ni zhu ba'i 'khor gyis bsdus //
NK118(se)001:521: grub chen brgyad sogs rgya bod mkhas pas bkral //
NK118(se)001:522: snga 'gyur ring lugs bka' gter grags pa dang //
NK118(se)001:523: gsar ma'i bzhed srol dpag tu med na yang //
NK118(se)001:524: rgyud sde spyi yi dam tshig 'dir 'chad do //
NK118(se)001:525: ngo bo sgo gsum thabs shes kyis zin par //
NK118(se)001:526: bsdams pa'i tshul khrims so so'i ring lugs bzhin //
NK118(se)001:527: dbye ba bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med bzhir //
NK118(se)001:528: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi so sor grangs nges pa //
NK118(se)001:529: dus kyi 'khor lor bshad pa gzhan du blta //
NK118(se)001:530: bla med lugs la brtul zhugs nyi shu lnga //
NK118(se)001:531: rigs lnga'i sdom pa rtsa ltung bcu bzhi dang //
NK118(se)001:532: sbom po dang ni rdzogs pa chen po'i srol //
NK118(se)001:533: dang po ma thob thob pa'i tshul bshad pa //
NK118(se)001:534: rdul tshon dang ni de bzhin b+ha ga dang //
NK118(se)001:535: kun rdzob don dam byang sems dkyil 'khor bzhir //
NK118(se)001:536: bum pa gsang ba shes rab bzhi pa'i dbang //
NK118(se)001:537: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i slob bur rim par bskur //
NK118(se)001:538: sad rmi gnyid 'thug snyoms 'jug gnas skabs bzhis //
NK118(se)001:539: bskyed pa'i sgo gsum shes bya'i dri ma sbyang //
NK118(se)001:540: bskyed rim gtum mo dpe don ye shes gnyis //
NK118(se)001:541: sgom dang sku bzhi thob pa'i nus rung bya //
NK118(se)001:542: dang po gnas gsum rdo rje gsum bskyed nas //
NK118(se)001:543: tha ma dbang bzhi yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe //
NK118(se)001:544: rig 'dzin sdom pa thob cing de yi rjes //
NK118(se)001:545: khas blangs sdom dang dam tshig bslab la 'bad //
NK118(se)001:546: bar du mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs bshad pa //
NK118(se)001:547: thog ma'i brtul zhugs dus kyi 'khor lo las //
NK118(se)001:548: gsod rdzun rku dang 'dod log chang 'thung ba //
NK118(se)001:549: spang bya bslab pa'i gzhi lnga spang zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)001:550: tshe lo kha na ma tho'i zas za dang //
NK118(se)001:551: ngan tshig 'byung po lha min chos bslab pa //
NK118(se)001:552: rnam pa lnga ni bya ba min lnga'o //
NK118(se)001:553: ba lang byis pa skyes pa bud med dang //
NK118(se)001:554: mchod rten bsnun pa gsod pa lnga ru grags //
NK118(se)001:555: dge grogs rje bo sangs rgyas dge 'dun dang //
NK118(se)001:556: bla mar khong khro sgom rnams 'khu ba lnga //
NK118(se)001:557: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya yul lnga la //
NK118(se)001:558: mig dang rna ba sna lce lus dbang lnga //
NK118(se)001:559: zhen par mi byed brtul zhugs nyer lnga'o //
NK118(se)001:560: thun mong gyur pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa lnga //
NK118(se)001:561: smon 'jug gnyis dang tshul khrims rnam pa gsum //
NK118(se)001:562: slob pa sangs rgyas rnal 'byor sdom pa'o //
NK118(se)001:563: rdor dril phyag rgya bla mar bzung rdo rje //
NK118(se)001:564: nor chos mi 'jigs byams sbyin rin chen 'byung //
NK118(se)001:565: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg 'dzin pad+ma'i rigs //
NK118(se)001:566: mchod gtor las rim 'dzin pa las kyi'o //
NK118(se)001:567: khyad par srog gcod rdo rje'i rigs yin te //
NK118(se)001:568: zhing bcu tshang dang rlung dang rtog pa yin //
NK118(se)001:569: rin chen rigs la ma byin len pa ni //
NK118(se)001:570: nor dang bud med theg chen zab mo'i chos //
NK118(se)001:571: rang dang gzhan don sgrub la dgongs pas gsungs //
NK118(se)001:572: pad+ma'i rigs la las chos dam tshig dang //
NK118(se)001:573: phyag rgya che ste bud med bsten par gsungs //
NK118(se)001:574: las kyi rigs la rdzun du smra gsungs pa //
NK118(se)001:575: bdag dang sems can mi dmigs bden med ston //
NK118(se)001:576: 'khor lo'i rigs la chang dang sha lnga dang //
NK118(se)001:577: yul kun bsten gsungs phyi nang gsang ba'i theg /
NK118(se)001:578: rim pa ma nyams spyod pa bla med lugs //
NK118(se)001:579: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi bstan pa ni //
NK118(se)001:580: slob dpon rnam gsum snying nas smod pa dang //
NK118(se)001:581: brnyas dang thugs dkrugs ltung ba'i sgo kun las //
NK118(se)001:582: shin tu lci phyir 'di nyid dang por bshad //
NK118(se)001:583: blang dor gnas ston bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' //
NK118(se)001:584: bla mas gsungs shing rang gis go bzhin du //
NK118(se)001:585: khyad gsod mi mthun spyod 'brel bka' 'das gnyis //
NK118(se)001:586: spyi ring nye dang nang 'dres spun la khros //
NK118(se)001:587: 'khon 'dzin phrag dog brnyas sogs gsum pa'o //
NK118(se)001:588: sems can bde ba kun dang bral na bsam //
NK118(se)001:589: snying nas byams pa btang ba bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)001:590: 'dod chags sems kyis gnas skabs ma yin par //
NK118(se)001:591: bsam bzhin khu ba 'byin dang sems can la //
NK118(se)001:592: byang chub sems bskyed btang ba lnga pa yin //
NK118(se)001:593: lam 'tshol mu stegs lam zhugs nyan rang dang //
NK118(se)001:594: lam chen theg chen grub mthar smod na drug /
NK118(se)001:595: snod dang cho ga ma byas ma rdzogs dang //
NK118(se)001:596: nyams dang zab mos 'jigs lngar gsang sgrog bdun //
NK118(se)001:597: phung lnga sangs rgyas lnga la brnyas pa yin //
NK118(se)001:598: smod dang gdung ba bskyed na brgyad pa yin //
NK118(se)001:599: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rang bzhin dag pa la //
NK118(se)001:600: dkri bar the tshom za bar dgu par bshad //
NK118(se)001:601: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu tshang ba nus bzhin du //
NK118(se)001:602: mi sgrol ba dang byams par byed na bcu //
NK118(se)001:603: ming sogs bral la dngos dang dngos med rtog /
NK118(se)001:604: rtog ges 'jal bar byed na bcu gcig pa'o //
NK118(se)001:605: dad gsum ldan pa'i sems can don mi byed //
NK118(se)001:606: sems mi bsrung dang bslu ba bcu gnyis pa //
NK118(se)001:607: skabs babs yo byad longs spyod dam tshig rdzas //
NK118(se)001:608: dus tshod 'brel kyang mi bsten bcu gsum pa //
NK118(se)001:609: spyi dang bye brag la ltos shes rab ma //
NK118(se)001:610: ngos lkog snying tshim smad go bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)001:611: da ni yan lag sbom po'i ltung ba bshad //
NK118(se)001:612: dbang dang dam tshig ma smin rig ma bsten //
NK118(se)001:613: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i dus su lus ngag rtsod //
NK118(se)001:614: ma gsungs rig mar rang stobs bdun rtsi len //
NK118(se)001:615: snod ldan slob mar gsang sngags mi ston dang //
NK118(se)001:616: dad ldan chos 'dri ba la chos gzhan ston //
NK118(se)001:617: nyan thos nang du zhag bdun longs par bsdad //
NK118(se)001:618: rnal 'byor ye shes mi ldan sngags par rlom //
NK118(se)001:619: snod min la bshad yan lag ltung ba brgyad //
NK118(se)001:620: bsnyen sogs ma byas dbang rab las sogs 'jug /
NK118(se)001:621: phyi chos mos la lus kyi phyag rgya bstan //
NK118(se)001:622: sdom pa gnyis kyi bcas las dgos med 'da' //
NK118(se)001:623: zhes sogs sbom po'i ltung ba du ma rnams //
NK118(se)001:624: yod kyang nyes pa chung zhes dus 'khor bshad //
NK118(se)001:625: khyad pa snga 'gyur rdzogs pa chen po'i srol //
NK118(se)001:626: rtsa ba bla ma'i sku gsung thugs gsum la //
NK118(se)001:627: dgu dgur phye ba nyi shu rtsa bdun dang //
NK118(se)001:628: yan lag dam tshig nyi shu rtsa lnga ni //
NK118(se)001:629: ta na ga na ma byin len dang rdzun //
NK118(se)001:630: ngag 'khyal rnams ni spyad par bya ba lnga //
NK118(se)001:631: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug nga rgyal dang //
NK118(se)001:632: phrag dog lnga ni mi spang dam tshig lnga //
NK118(se)001:633: dri chen dri chu rak+ta m+aam sa dang //
NK118(se)001:634: rdo rje zil pa dang du blang ba lnga //
NK118(se)001:635: phung lnga 'byung lnga yul lnga dbang po lnga //
NK118(se)001:636: kha dog lnga rnams lha ru shes pa lnga //
NK118(se)001:637: de bzhin gshegs dang rdo rje rin po che //
NK118(se)001:638: pad+ma las rigs bsgrub bya lnga rnams ni //
NK118(se)001:639: dus tshod 'brel ba'i spyod pas dgongs pa blang //
NK118(se)001:640: de sogs dam tshig rnam gzhag mang gsungs pa //
NK118(se)001:641: rtsa ba yan lag bcas 'dir ma 'dus med //
NK118(se)001:642: mdor na rang lus rdo rje gsum shes na //
NK118(se)001:643: sngags kyi dam tshigs sa ya 'bum sde 'dus //
NK118(se)001:644: skye ba'i rten ni nyin bzhin bram ze gsod //
NK118(se)001:645: mtshams med lnga byed la sogs kun la'o //
NK118(se)001:646: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK118(se)001:647: ltung mtshams mi shes bla ma sogs mi gus //
NK118(se)001:648: bag med spyod cing nyon mong mang ba bzhi //
NK118(se)001:649: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhir thogs med bzhed //
NK118(se)001:650: de yi gnyen por bslab byar bslab pa dang //
NK118(se)001:651: kun la gus bskyed rtag par dran shes bsten //
NK118(se)001:652: nyon mongs gang che'i gnyen po 'bad de bslab //
NK118(se)001:653: spang bya bzhi'i steng brjed ngas dran mi gsal //
NK118(se)001:654: gnyis bsnan dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu drug ces //
NK118(se)001:655: dpal ldan sdom pa'i rgyud las gsal bar gsungs //
NK118(se)001:656: kun la yul bsam sbyor ba mthar thug gam //
NK118(se)001:657: kun slong nyon mongs gang 'gal der shes dang //
NK118(se)001:658: lus ngag sbyor byas dngos gzhi bar chod pa //
NK118(se)001:659: ma 'khrul spyad dang 'gyod med bshags tshad 'das //
NK118(se)001:660: pham pa zhes brjod dngos gzhi ma tshang na //
NK118(se)001:661: thun 'das ltung ba zhes brjod lhag ma ltar //
NK118(se)001:662: rim pas dman na sbom po ltung byed dang //
NK118(se)001:663: nyes byas ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan shes par bya //
NK118(se)001:664: na dang dbang nyams bya ba gzhan gyis dang //
NK118(se)001:665: don chen skye med brtan dang dgos ldan dang //
NK118(se)001:666: nus rnyed gnang dang bka' bsgo bar chad las //
NK118(se)001:667: nyes pa med ces snying po rgyan las gsungs //
NK118(se)001:668: de ltar nyin mtshan thun la lan drug tu //
NK118(se)001:669: spang blang dam tshig gnas la sgrims te dpyad //
NK118(se)001:670: drug cha 'das na thun tshod 'das zhes bya //
NK118(se)001:671: zhag gcig zla gcig lo gcig lo gnyis 'das //
NK118(se)001:672: 'gal nyams 'das ral zhes brjod de dag kyang //
NK118(se)001:673: snying nas bshags na gsor rung phyi rim lci //
NK118(se)001:674: lo gsum 'das na gsor mi rung ba yin //
NK118(se)001:675: dbang bdun thob la lha grangs re re la //
NK118(se)001:676: bzlas pa sum khri drug stong byas pas sbyang //
NK118(se)001:677: bum gsung thob nyams sngon du chad las sbyang //
NK118(se)001:678: de rjes dkyil 'khor zhugs la dbang bzhi len //
NK118(se)001:679: sher dbang tshig dbang thob nyams bskyed rim dang //
NK118(se)001:680: 'pho med tshul khrims rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang //
NK118(se)001:681: rang rgyud byin rlabs ma gtogs gzhan mi 'dag /'gal na tshogs 'khor nyams na bdog pas bskang //
NK118(se)001:682: 'das na bu dang chung ma nor sogs dang //
NK118(se)001:683: ral na rang gi srog gis gso bar bshad //
NK118(se)001:684: snying po rgyan las gso ba'i cho ga ni //
NK118(se)001:685: tshogs zhing la bshags dral ba'i sngags rgya dang //
NK118(se)001:686: bkru ba'i rim pa gtum mo'i mes sreg dang //
NK118(se)001:687: mi dmigs bsgom dang dbang bzhi blang ba dang //
NK118(se)001:688: tshogs su zhu dang rten la smre ba dang //
NK118(se)001:689: man+dala 'bul dang mchod rten bya ba dang //
NK118(se)001:690: me la sbyang dang gtor ma gtong ba dang //
NK118(se)001:691: gsang sngags bzla dang zab mo'i bsam gtan dang //
NK118(se)001:692: srog skyob bka' klog bla ma bsten pa dang //
NK118(se)001:693: bdag 'jug rgyal ba'i yig brgya dus bzang bzla //
NK118(se)001:694: phung po gsum pa rdor sems bla ma dang //
NK118(se)001:695: thig le phra mo'i rnal 'byor bsgom pas gso //
NK118(se)001:696: glang chen rab 'bog rgyud las gsungs pa yi //
NK118(se)001:697: rnal 'byor spyi khrus 'gyod tshangs dong sprug gi //
NK118(se)001:698: bshags pas mi 'dag med phyir nyams su blang //
NK118(se)001:699: ma bshags tshe 'dir yid mi 'ong bas mnar //
NK118(se)001:700: phyi ma rdo rje'i dmyal ba zhes bya ba //
NK118(se)001:701: mnar med do zla med pa'i gnas su skye //
NK118(se)001:702: ma nyams ring mtha' skye ba bcu drug gam //
NK118(se)001:703: myur na tshe 'adi'am 'chi kha bar do ru //
NK118(se)001:704: thun mong grub pa brgyad dang dbang phyug brgyad //
NK118(se)001:705: mchog gi dngos grub kha sbyor bdun ldan thob //
NK118(se)001:706: de phyir rang gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK118(se)001:707: gsang sngags rig 'dzin sdom pa'i rim par phye ba ste bzhi pa'o ////
NK118(se)001:708: de lta'i sdom gsum gang zag rgyud gcig la //
NK118(se)001:709: rang ldog ma 'dres dgag dgos yongs su rdzogs //
NK118(se)001:710: ngo bo gnas 'gyur yon tan yar ldan pas //
NK118(se)001:711: gnad kyis mi 'gal dus skabs gang gtsor spyad //
NK118(se)001:712: de yang blang yul bsam pa cho ga rnams //
NK118(se)001:713: so so'i nges phyir rang ldog ma 'dres yin //
NK118(se)001:714: dgag bya nyon mongs dgos pa mi 'ching bar //
NK118(se)001:715: rang rang lam gyi ngos nas yongs su rdzogs //
NK118(se)001:716: spong bsgyur lam du byed pa so so yang //
NK118(se)001:717: nyon mongs rang mtshan spong bar mkhas rnams mthun //
NK118(se)001:718: so thar kun slong sems bskyed kyis zin na //
NK118(se)001:719: nyes spyod sdom pa zhes bya'i tshul khrims yin //
NK118(se)001:720: dbang thob rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sdom par 'gyur //
NK118(se)001:721: de phyir ngo bo gnas 'gyur yin no zhes //
NK118(se)001:722: 'bum phrag lnga pa'i lung gis gsal bar grub //
NK118(se)001:723: 'jig rten rnal 'byor rnal 'byor blo khyad kyis //
NK118(se)001:724: gong ma gong mas gnod phyir 'og ma yi //
NK118(se)001:725: yon tan yar ldan 'og ma zil gyis gnon //
NK118(se)001:726: 'du shes gsum gyis 'khrig na rnal 'byor de //
NK118(se)001:727: yul bsam sbyor ba mthar thug ma tshang bas //
NK118(se)001:728: rmi lam ji bzhin gnad kyis 'gal mi srid //
NK118(se)001:729: sdig to mi dge'i phyogs dang tshogs pa'i gseb //
NK118(se)001:730: 'og ma gtsor spyod 'dod pas dben pa dang //
NK118(se)001:731: spyod pa'i dus dang dben par gsang sngags spyad //
NK118(se)001:732: nang ma 'dom na ma 'dres yongs rdzogs bsrung //
NK118(se)001:733: 'dom na dgag dgos brtsi zhes mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK118(se)001:734: las dang po dang rnal 'byor grub thob dang //
NK118(se)001:735: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyod pa gang yin pa //
NK118(se)001:736: dus tshod 'brel bar dgos zhes dus 'khor bshad //
NK118(se)001:737: yon tan gzhi rten so thar gang nus steng //
NK118(se)001:738: byang chub sems bskyed sngags kyi yan lag yin //
NK118(se)001:739: smin byed dbang thob sdom gsum mig ltar bsrung //
NK118(se)001:740: gdan gsum lha ru shes pa'i bskyed rim dang //
NK118(se)001:741: mtshan bcas mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs rim bsgom //
NK118(se)001:742: nye rgyu'i spyod pas rim bzhin mtshan sbyar na //
NK118(se)001:743: 'adi'am 'chi kha dang ni bar do ru //
NK118(se)001:744: rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing du rdzogs 'tshang rgya //
NK118(se)001:745: sdom gsum spyir dpyad pa'i rim par phye ba ste lnga pa'o ////
NK118(se)001:746: ding sang ma sbyangs mu cor smra ba brgyas //
NK118(se)001:747: rang gi ye shes rdul tsam ma rtogs par //
NK118(se)001:748: rang bzo'i cho gas rmongs rnams tshim pa'i dus //
NK118(se)001:749: skyabs de bsams kyin snying nas mchi ma bku //
NK118(se)001:750: mdo sngags lam rnams mu med 'gro ba'i phyiir //
NK118(se)001:751: tshang lang ma nor lam 'di rgyal bas gsungs //
NK118(se)001:752: gangs can 'di na de dag phyogs rer 'dzin //
NK118(se)001:753: gcig tu sems kyang sdom gsum ming tsam lus //
NK118(se)001:754: 'di ni mkhas grub du ma'i legs bshad las //
NK118(se)001:755: sgrims po'i blo yis phyogs gcig dag tu bkod //
NK118(se)001:756: de phyir nongs pa'i dri ma med snyam rlom //
NK118(se)001:757: dge des kun bzang go 'phang myur thob shog /
NK118(se)001:758: ces sdom gsum rnam nges tshig gis rim par phye
NK118(se)001:759: ba 'di gangs ri'i phreng bas bskor ba'i yul ljongs
NK118(se)001:760: lho phyogs kyi rgyud du byung ba nges par 'byung
NK118(se)001:761: ba'i bsam pa can mnga' ris kyi pan+di ta pad+ma
NK118(se)001:762: dbang gi rgyal pos bkod pa /
NK118(se)001:763: phyogs dus thams cad du rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
